ao nosso grupo de estudos, Rachel?

38
00:01:08,443 --> 00:01:09,945
Claro, Danny.

39
00:01:10,821 --> 00:01:12,239
Sou o Derek.

40
00:01:12,322 --> 00:01:14,324
